<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Shopping Cart</title>
    <style>
        body {
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
            background-image: url("https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1561715276-a2d087060f1d?q=80&w=1770&auto=format&fit=crop&ixlib=rb-4.0.3&ixid=M3wxMjA3fDB8MHxwaG90by1wYWdlfHx8fGVufDB8fHx8fA%3D%3D");
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            /* box-shadow: inset 0 0 7rem rgba(52, 52, 52, 0.5); */
            color: #fff;
            line-height: 1.8;
        }
        nav {
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            padding: 1rem;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5); /* Darken the background */
        }
        nav h1 a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
        }
        nav ul {
            list-style-type: none;
            margin: 0;
            padding: 0;
            display: flex;
        }
        nav ul li {
            margin-right: 1rem;
        }
        nav ul li a {
            color: #fff;
            text-decoration: none;
            padding: 0.5rem 1rem;
            border-radius: 5px;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        nav ul li a:hover {
            background-color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
        }
        .container {
            max-width: 1200px;
            margin: 11rem auto;
            padding: 1rem;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.45); /* Darken the container */
            border-radius: 10px;
            box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.3);
            color: #fff; /* Text color inside container */
        }
        h2 {
            margin-left: 30.8rem;
            color: #fff;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }
        p {
            margin-left: 30rem;
            margin-bottom: 0.5rem;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>
    <nav>
        <h1><a href="#">Shopping Cart</a></h1>
        <ul>
            <li style="font-weight: bolder;"><a href="#">Home</a></li>
            <li style="font-weight: bolder;"><a href="/products">Products</a></li>
            <li style="font-weight: bolder;"><a href="/login">Login</a></li>
            <li style="font-weight: bolder;"><a href="/register">Register</a></li>
        </ul>
    </nav>

    <div class="container">
        <h2>Shopping Cart</h2>
        <p style="margin-left: 29rem;">Welcome to the shopping cart!</p>
        <p style="margin-left: 27rem;">Jump right in and explore our products.</p>
        <p style="margin-left: 25rem;">Feel free to add your own and comment on others!</p>
    </div>
</body>
</html>
